---
title: Bacon & Thyme Crusted Chicken Breast with Garlic Greens
description: Pangrattato (Italian for sautéed breadcrumbs) is a great way to add a delightfully delicious crunch to any dish! Tonight, we’re getting fancy on you with succulent chicken, topped with a bacon and thyme pangrattato. Level it up with a side of garlic-infused greens for a truly gourmet dinner – without the hefty price tag.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bacon-thyme-crusted-chicken-breast-e682d4fd.jpg
